'''莎麗·海明斯'''（{{lang-en|Sally Hemings}}，{{bd|1773年||1835年}}），是[[美國總統|美國總統]][[托馬斯·傑佛遜|托馬斯·傑佛遜]]所擁有的非裔[[奴隸|奴隸]]和情婦，亦是傑佛遜原配[[瑪莎·傑佛遜|瑪莎·傑佛遜]]的同父異母妹妹。歷史學家普遍認為傑佛遜與莎麗·海明斯存在長時間的性關係，而傑佛遜亦是她6名孩子的父親<ref name="stockman">{{Cite news |url= https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/16/us/sally-hemings-exhibit-monticello.html |title=Monticello Is Done Avoiding Jefferson's Relationship With Sally Hemings |last=Stockman |first=Farah |date=June 16, 2018 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |access-date=July 15, 2018}}</ref>。

== 早年生活 ==
莎麗·海明斯的父親{{le|約翰·韋爾斯|John Wayles}}是位白人地主，其母親{{le|貝蒂·海明斯|Betty Hemings}}一出世已經是奴隸。她的外祖母帕台尼娜為100％非裔血統，外祖父約翰·海明斯則是英國裔的船長<ref name="madisonstatement">{{Cite web |title=Jefferson's Blood – The Memoirs of Madison Hemings |work=[[Frontline_(American_TV_program)|Frontline]] |publisher=[[Public_Broadcasting_System|Public Broadcasting System]] / [[WGBH-TV|WGBH-TV]] |date=2000 |url= https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/jefferson/cron/1873march.html}}</ref>。約翰·海明斯曾經嘗試為帕台尼娜及貝蒂贖身，但遭到當時的地主所拒絕<ref name="madisonstatement" />。在地主過世之後，其女兒繼承了帕台尼娜及貝蒂的擁有權，直到她嫁給韋爾斯。韋爾斯視貝蒂為[[妾侍|妾侍]]，二人生了6個孩子，莎麗是最小的一個<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.monticello.org/site/plantation-and-slavery/elizabeth-hemings |title=Elizabeth Hemings |work=Monticello.org |publisher=[[Thomas_Jefferson_Foundation|Thomas Jefferson Foundation]] |access-date=January 7, 2012}} Says that Betty Hemings's children by John Wayles were Robert, James, Thenia, Critta, Peter, and Sally.</ref>{{sfn|Gordon-Reed|p=80|2008}}。韋爾斯死後，其女兒瑪莎及女婿托馬斯·傑佛遜繼承了莎麗（當時還是襁褓中的嬰兒）和另外百多名奴隸及{{convert|11000|acres}}土地的擁有權<ref name="autogenerated3">{{cite web |url= http://wiki.monticello.org/mediawiki/index.php/John_Wayles |title=John Wayles |work=Monticello.org |publisher=[[Thomas_Jefferson_Foundation|Thomas Jefferson Foundation]] |access-date=January 25, 2012 |archive-url= https://archive.is/20120722015323/http://wiki.monticello.org/mediawiki/index.php/John_Wayles |archive-date=July 22, 2012}}</ref>{{sfn|Gordon-Reed|p=92|2008}}。及後，莎麗被帶到傑佛遜在蒙蒂塞洛的家中工作<ref name="autogenerated3" />。

